Class BaselineTransformerParams

  • java.lang.Object
    • marytts.signalproc.adaptation.BaselineParams
      • marytts.signalproc.adaptation.BaselineTransformerParams
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    JointGMMTransformerParams, WeightedCodebookTransformerParams

    public class BaselineTransformerParams
extends BaselineParams
    Baseline class for voice conversion transformation parameters All specific implementations of transformation stage of a given voice conversion algorithm should use a parameter set that is derived from this class
    Author:
    Oytun Türk
